com.googlecode.jmxtrans.model
Class Query

java.lang.Object
  com.googlecode.jmxtrans.model.Query

public class Query
extends java.lang.Object

Represents a JMX Query to ask for obj, attr and one or more keys. Once the query has been executed, it'll have a list of results.
